column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.petroMag_g, p.petroMag_r, petroMag_i, p.petroMagErr_g, p.petroMagErr_r, p.petroMagErr_i, p.petroR5#_g, p.petroR5#_r, p.petroR5#_i, p.petroR5#Err_g, p.petroR5#Err_r, p.petroR5#Err_i, p.petroR9#_g, p.petroR9#_r, p.petroR9#_i, p.petroR9#Err_g, p.petroR9#Err_r, p.petroR9#Err_i, IS# (p.type, #) AS type, IS# (s.z, #) AS z, IS# (s.zErr, #) AS zErr, f.kk_g, f.kk_r, f.kk_i, f.airmass_g, f.airmass_r, f.airmass_i f.aa_g, f.aa_r, f.aa_i INTO mydb.hw1_sh_ext FROM Galaxy AS p LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecObj s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID JOIN Field f ON f.fieldID = p.fieldID WHERE s.z BETWEEN # AND # AND p.petroR5#Err_r < # AND s.zConf > #
